  dialogue:
  - 'X: Yeah, it''s all starting to become real.

    Heck, I nearly dropped my gauntlet
    when putting it on!'
  - 'Y: Good. Nerves mean its important to you. You''re gonna kick ass today Max,
    I know you will.

'
  - 'Here, I''ll be watching, found a little backdoor into the server you''ll be
    testing on. I''ve got your back bro. Always.

'
  - Breathe, let me walk you through something that helped me my test day. Eyes closed,
    deep breaths, and pretend you're walking on this table.
